## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="aa2e5-102">Il <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> oggetto ha un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> proprietà che possono essere assegnati a una con esecuzione prolungata <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> nel gestore per il <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceView.ContextCreating> evento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="aa2e5-102">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> object has a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> property that can be assigned to a long-running <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> in the handler for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceView.ContextCreating> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="aa2e5-103">Per altre informazioni, vedere [gestione del ciclo di vita oggetto contesto (EntityDataSource)](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/67bc2486-112c-47c3-b23f-0297f7ac2160).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="aa2e5-103">For more information, see [Object Context Life-Cycle Management (EntityDataSource)](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/67bc2486-112c-47c3-b23f-0297f7ac2160).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="aa2e5-104">L'esempio seguente illustra la creazione di un <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> variabili del <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> oggetto e la relativa assegnazione il <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> proprietà del <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> oggetto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="aa2e5-104">The following example shows the creation of an <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> variable of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> object and its assignment to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> object.</span></span>  
  
```  
public partial class _Default : System.Web.UI.Page  
    {  
        AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities objCtx =  
            new AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities();  
  
        protected void EntityDataSource2_ContextCreating(object sender,   
            EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs e)  
        {  
            e.Context = objCtx;  
        }  
    }  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="aa2e5-107">Il <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> proprietà può essere assegnata a una con esecuzione prolungata <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> nel gestore per il <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceView.ContextCreating> evento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="aa2e5-107">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> property can be assigned to a long-running <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> in the handler for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceView.ContextCreating> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="aa2e5-108">Per altre informazioni, vedere [gestione del ciclo di vita oggetto contesto (EntityDataSource)](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/67bc2486-112c-47c3-b23f-0297f7ac2160).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="aa2e5-108">For more information, see [Object Context Life-Cycle Management (EntityDataSource)](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/67bc2486-112c-47c3-b23f-0297f7ac2160).</span></span>  
  
   
  
